</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_475" id="237r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_475_r1l13">Görgen <expan>Cʒeng<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒu <expan>Roſemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_475_r1l14"><expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> Görg / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>Cʒeng<ex>er</ex>s</expan> frıdbrıf </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_475_r1l16">geſant habt / Alſo ſchıcken wir ew <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> frıdbrıf gen Jm <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_475_r1l17">vnd als Jr <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>t</expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> deʒ tags <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> der cʒü Herſprugk ſeın ſol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_475_r1l18">daʒ wir ew <expan>laſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>wiſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> auf welıche cʒeit es vns güt dunk </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_475_r1l19">das man den tag mache / . Alſo 
<del rend="strikethrough"> g </del> dewcht vns güt daʒ der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_475_r1l20">tag wer auf ſant Veits tag / <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> in dreyen tagen darnach </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_475_r1l21">vnd <expan>bitt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ewr erberkeit / Auf welıchen tag Jr darcʒü <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_475_r1l22">wöllet / daʒ Jr vns das <expan>cʒeitlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vor cʒevvıſſen tün wöllet / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_475_r1l23"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ıııj̃ . <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Bonifacij / . </ab>
</div>
<div type="cedula"><ab facs="#facs_475_r1l25">Cedula / Auch <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_475_r1l26"><expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> das lon <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_475" id="237r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Görgen <expan>Czeng<ex>er</ex></expan> czu <expan>Rosemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> Görg, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                                <expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>Czeng<ex>er</ex>s</expan> fridbrif gesant habt, also schicken wir ew
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> fridbrif gen im
                            <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>; und als ir <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>t</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> dez tags <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, der czü
                        Hersprugk sein sol, daz wir ew <expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan>, auf weliche czeit es uns güt dunk, das man
                        den tag mache, also dewcht uns güt, daz der tag wer <app><note><q type="date">auf sant Veits tag</q>15.06.1412</note></app>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <app><note><q type="date">in dreyen tagen darnach</q>18.06.1412</note></app>; und
                                <expan>bitt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ewr erberkeit, auf welichen tag ir
                        darczü <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet, daz ir uns das
                                <expan>czeitlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vor cze wissen tün wöllet.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Bonifacii.
                    </ab>
</div>
<div type="cedula">
<ab>Cedula<lb/> Auch <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> das lon <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n.</expan>
</ab>
</div>
